	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=136630><span id= >Ziad</span></a><br><span id=notbold>15 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Excellent [4.50]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>The Glowing Worm Bile still drop, but they seem to be semi-rare.&nbsp;&nbsp;In the last 3 days I have managed to get 4 of them.  The definately drop from the Elder Shardworms and also the Young Shardworms.  As far as the worm glowing in the dark, that is misleading.  Actually, the ground beneath and around the worms light up as if they had lightstone.  At night, this can easily be seen.  They look like rabbit meat, but they cannot be stacked.  Hope this helps.<br><br>Marim Mornmist of Sanctus Covenir<br>51 Enchanter<br>Povar</p>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
